The '''Ransar Rhal Insignia''' was a [[Bitthævrian/Legends|Bitthævrian]] decoration. Heroic Bitthævrian [[Aul Tarrus Vishav]] was decored with this insignia after saving Quaal Tavier Catharius's life, which almost guaranteed Vishav's place as Catharius's successor.

